(49, 119, 'Sources', 'Ø§Ù„Ù…ØµØ§Ø¯Ø±', '&amp;lt;div&amp;gt;&amp;lt;font size=&amp;quot;5&amp;quot;&amp;gt;Sources:&amp;lt;/font&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&amp;lt;font size=&amp;quot;3&amp;quot;&amp;gt;CDC&amp;lt;/font&amp;gt;&amp;lt;div&amp;gt;&amp;lt;font size=&amp;quot;3&amp;quot;&amp;gt;https://www.cdc.gov/ncbddd/autism&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/font&amp;gt;&amp;lt;div&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;', '&amp;lt;div style=&amp;quot;text-align: right;&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;font size=&amp;quot;5&amp;quot;&amp;gt;Ø§Ù„Ù…ØµØ§Ø¯Ø±&amp;lt;/font&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&amp;lt;div style=&amp;quot;text-align: right;&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&amp;lt;div style=&amp;quot;text-align: right;&amp;quot;&amp;gt;https://www.cdc.gov/ncbddd/autism&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;'),
(44, 119, 'Treatment ', 'Ø¹Ù„Ø§Ø¬ Ø§Ùˆ Ù…Ø¹Ø§Ù…Ù„Ø©', '&amp;lt;h3 style=&amp;quot;margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; line-height: 1.3; font-family: Merriweather, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;font size=&amp;quot;5&amp;quot;&amp;gt;Treatment&amp;lt;/font&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/h3&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p style=&amp;quot;margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &amp;amp;quot;Open Sans&amp;amp;quot;, apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, &amp;amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;amp;quot;, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;&amp;quot;&amp;gt;There is currently no cure for ASD. However, research shows that early intervention treatment services can improve a child&rsquo;s development.&amp;lt;span style=&amp;quot;position: relative; font-size: 0.65em; line-height: 1.15; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;a href=&amp;quot;https://www.cdc.gov/ncbddd/autism/facts.html#ref&amp;quot; style=&amp;quot;color: rgb(7, 82, 144);&amp;quot;&amp;gt;2, 3&amp;lt;/a&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&amp;amp;nbsp;Early intervention services help children from birth to 3 years old (36 months) learn important skills. Services can include therapy to help the child talk, walk, and interact with others. Therefore, it is important to talk to your child&rsquo;s doctor as soon as possible if you think your child has ASD or other developmental problem.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p style=&amp;quot;margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &amp;amp;quot;Open Sans&amp;amp;quot;, apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, &amp;amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;amp;quot;, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;&amp;quot;&amp;gt;Even if your child has not been diagnosed with an ASD, he or she may be eligible for early intervention treatment services. The&amp;amp;nbsp;&amp;lt;a href=&amp;quot;http://idea.ed.gov/&amp;quot; class=&amp;quot;tp-link-policy&amp;quot; data-domain-ext=&amp;quot;gov&amp;quot; style=&amp;quot;color: rgb(7, 82, 144); text-decoration-line: underline;&amp;quot;&amp;gt;Individuals with Disabilities Education Act (IDEA)&amp;lt;span class=&amp;quot;sr-only&amp;quot; style=&amp;quot;white-space: nowrap; text-decoration-line: none !important;&amp;quot;&amp;gt;external icon&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&amp;lt;span class=&amp;quot;fi cdc-icon-external x16 fill-external&amp;quot; aria-hidden=&amp;quot;true&amp;quot; style=&amp;quot;text-decoration: inherit; position: relative; display: inline-block; vertical-align: inherit; margin-right: 5px; margin-left: 5px;&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/a&amp;gt;&amp;amp;nbsp;says that children under the age of 3 years (36 months) who are at risk of having developmental delays may be eligible for services. These services are provided through an early intervention system in your state. Through this system, you can ask for an evaluation.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p style=&amp;quot;margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &amp;amp;quot;Open Sans&amp;amp;quot;, apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, &amp;amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;amp;quot;, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;&amp;quot;&amp;gt;In addition, treatment for particular symptoms, such as speech therapy for language delays, often does not need to wait for a formal ASD diagnosis.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;', '&amp;lt;div style=&amp;quot;text-align: right;&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;font size=&amp;quot;5&amp;quot; style=&amp;quot;background-color: rgb(0, 153, 204);&amp;quot;&amp;gt;Ø¹Ù„Ø§Ø¬ Ø§Ùˆ Ù…Ø¹Ø§Ù…Ù„Ø©&amp;lt;/font&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&amp;lt;div style=&amp;quot;text-align: right;&amp;quot;&amp;gt;Ù„Ø§ ÙŠÙˆØ¬Ø¯ Ø­Ø§Ù„ÙŠØ§ Ø¹Ù„Ø§Ø¬ Ù„Ø§Ø¶Ø·Ø±Ø§Ø¨ Ø·ÙŠÙ Ø§Ù„ØªÙˆØ­Ø¯. ÙˆÙ…Ø¹ Ø°Ù„Ùƒ ØŒ ØªØ¸Ù‡Ø± Ø§Ù„Ø£Ø¨Ø­Ø§Ø« Ø£Ù† Ø®Ø¯Ù…Ø§Øª Ø§Ù„ØªØ¯Ø®Ù„ Ø§Ù„Ù…Ø¨ÙƒØ± Ø§Ù„Ø¹Ù„Ø§Ø¬ ÙŠÙ…ÙƒÙ† Ø£Ù† ØªØ­Ø³Ù† Ù…Ù† Ù†Ù…Ùˆ Ø§Ù„Ø·ÙÙ„. 2 ØŒ 3 Ø®Ø¯Ù…Ø§Øª Ø§Ù„ØªØ¯Ø®Ù„ Ø§Ù„Ù…Ø¨ÙƒØ± ØªØ³Ø§Ø¹Ø¯ Ø§Ù„Ø£Ø·ÙØ§Ù„ Ù…Ù†Ø° Ø§Ù„ÙˆÙ„Ø§Ø¯Ø© Ø­